High Fidelity (hifi) is an early-stage technology lab experimenting with Virtual Worlds and VR. In addition to our full-time San Francisco-based team (we're hiring), we also use independent, paid developers on http://worklist.net (signup is free; join if you'd like to help) to build hifi's many components.
